    "description": [
      "<hr/>",
      "# &&eLarge Steam Boiler",
      "<br/>",
      "  Need a steamy upgrade? I know I do! The /b/Large Steam Boiler/b/ is an upgraded version of the smaller bronze and steel boilers. /6/It uses fuel 8 times faster/6/ than the Furnace, but it produces /6/256 mb/t of steam/6/ when at max temperature. Make sure you don't forget to provide it /b/Water/b/!",
      "<br/>",
      "  The main block you'll need is /b/Bronze Plated Bricks/b/, but you'll also need other blocks shown in your REI. The /b/Large Steam Boiler/b/ is comprised of one layer of /b/Heatproof Machine Casings/b/ with layers of /6/Bronze Plated Bricks/6/ and /6/Pipe Machine Casings/6/.",
      "<br/>",
      "  The Controller is on the second layer, on top of the /b/Heatproof Machine Casings/b/. /6/Don't forget you can use your /b/Wrench/b/ to show the shape of the multiblock and placement of the blocks needed for it/6/. The required hatches must be placed on the bottom layer. You'll need a way to input water and a solid fuel, as well as a way to extract /b/Steam/b/.",
      "<hr/>"
    ],
